### ============================================================
### TICKET TYPES API REQUESTS
### Base URL: http://localhost:8000/v1/ticket-types
### ============================================================

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/v1
@authToken = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
@ticketTypeId = 1
@eventId = 1

### ============================================================
### PUBLIC ROUTES (No Authentication Required)
### ============================================================

