### ============================================================
### PROTECTED ROUTES (Authentication Required - Organizer)
### ============================================================

### Create Ticket Type
POST {{baseUrl}}/ticket-types
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
    "event_id": 1,
    "name": "Early Bird",
    "description": "Discounted early bird ticket - limited availability",
    "price": 35.00,
    "quantity": 200,
    "sale_start": "2025-01-01T00:00:00",
    "sale_end": "2025-03-31T23:59:59",
    "min_per_order": 1,
    "max_per_order": 5
}

### Expected Response:
