### Update Ticket Type
PUT {{baseUrl}}/ticket-types/{{ticketTypeId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
    "name": "Updated Ticket Name",
    "description": "Updated description",
    "price": 60.00,
    "quantity": 600,
    "sale_end": "2025-06-14T23:59:59"
}

### Expected Response:
# {
#     "success": true,
#     "message": "Ticket type updated successfully",
#     "data": {
#         "ticket_type": {...}
#     }
# }

###

### Delete Ticket Type
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/ticket-types/{{ticketTypeId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Expected Response:
# {
#     "success": true,
#     "message": "Ticket type deleted successfully"
# }

###
